<h6 id="green"> 
About Us
</h6>
<br/>
We provide fee based hiking and camping services and services in
support of our parent charity's charitable hiking and camping youth
programs.
<BR>
We also provide adult hiking programs through the 
<a href="http://www.waynecommunityprograms.com/courses/dsp_course_section.cfm?int_course_section_id=82&int_department_id=28&int_school_id=21">
Wayne Township</a> and the 
<a href="http://rcs.school.ridgewood.k12.nj.us"> 
Village of Ridgewood Adult Community</a> Schools
 and private fee based hiking and camping to both adults and families.  
<BR>
<BR>
Our goal is to introduce the public to the fun and wonders of outdoor
recreation and to teach the importance of protecting the environment through
safe and controlled hiking and camping experiences while instilling the
confidence to undertake independent outdoor adventures.
